Lingua::Any::Numbers
====================

Converts numbers into (any available language) string.

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake test
   nmake install

DEPENDENCIES

      Lingua::EN::Numbers
      Test::More

RECOMMENDED MODULES

      Lingua::AF::Numbers
      Lingua::BG::Numbers
      Lingua::EU::Numbers
      Lingua::FR::Numbers
      Lingua::HU::Numbers
      Lingua::IT::Numbers
      Lingua::JA::Numbers
      Lingua::NL::Numbers
      Lingua::PL::Numbers
      Lingua::TR::Numbers
      Lingua::ZH::Numbers

